<p>Place and Time</p>

<ol>
  <li>Best time for having a lecture is 11 am.
 (not too early and not after lunch)</li>
  <li>The place should be well lit.</li>
  <li>The place should be seen and checked before the lecture.</li>
  <li>The place should not be full less than a half, it must be chosen according to the amount of listeners.</li>
</ol>

<p>Tools
