    </blockquote>

    <p>Example:</p>

    <blockquote>
      <p>Â â€œWell, we had 2 VARCHAR, fields from the M2S legacy system that were being concatenated before the websphere interface batch job â€¦ bla bla bla â€¦ The SAP iDocs were correctly configured, so, bla bla blaâ€¦ Eventually we noticed that the fields were being truncated â€¦ bla bla blaâ€¦ so finally, we were able to fix it by â€¦womp womp wompâ€¦Â Â yeah, so now it works.â€</p>
