    <p>Which experience is better?</p>

    <p>6b. Letâ€™s now do a second thought experiment, this time imagining that you were hungry, but had anÂ unidentifiableÂ craving. How would you hope the conversation to go?</p>

    <p>â€œYouâ€™re here because youâ€™re hungry. What are you in the mood for?â€
